# Facebook Ad Campaign Analysis with SQL  

## ðŸ“ Project Description  
This project analyzes the performance of Facebook ad campaigns using SQL.  
Data is sourced from the `facebook_ads_basic_daily` table, and key metrics such as **CPC, CPM, CTR, and ROMI** are calculated.  

##GÃ¶revler:
#AÅŸaÄŸÄ±daki verileri facebook_ads_basic_daily tablosundan alacak bir SQL sorgusu yazÄ±n:
 	- ad_date (reklamÄ±n gÃ¶rÃ¼ntÃ¼lendiÄŸi tarih)
 	- campaign_id (kampanyanÄ±n benzersiz tanÄ±mlayÄ±cÄ±sÄ±)
#AÅŸaÄŸÄ±daki gÃ¶stergeler (metrikler) iÃ§in tarih (ad_date) ve kampanya kimliÄŸine (campaign_id) gÃ¶re toplanmÄ±ÅŸ (aggregate edilmiÅŸ) alanlarÄ± oluÅŸturun: 
  - toplam maliyet
	- gÃ¶sterim sayÄ±sÄ±
	- tÄ±klama sayÄ±sÄ±
	- total value deÄŸeri
#Toplanan harcama ve dÃ¶nÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼m oranlarÄ±nÄ± kullanarak her tarih ve kampanya kimliÄŸi iÃ§in aÅŸaÄŸÄ±daki metrikleri hesaplayÄ±n:
 	- CPC
